      <title>泰国将扩大预算缺口 42 亿美元以刺激经济增长</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-02/thailand-to-widen-2025-budget-gap-by-4-2-billion-to-spur-growth</link>
