    <item>
      <title>戛纳游艇遭遇事件引发日内瓦银行家涉嫌 18 亿美元 1MDB 欺诈</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-02/cannes-yacht-encounter-sparked-bankers-alleged-1-8-billion-1mdb-fraud</link>
      <description><![CDATA[事情始于2009年夏天在戛纳海岸的一艘游艇上举行的一次会议。新当选的马来西亚总理应商人刘特佐和沙特裔瑞士商人塔里克·奥贝德的邀请登上了游艇。这些人聚集在一起探讨马来西亚新经济发展基金 1MDB 的交易。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-02/cannes-yacht-encounter-sparked-bankers-alleged-1-8-billion-1mdb-fraud</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 02 Apr 2024 04:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>卢比处于四年低点引发干预和加息讨论</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-02/rupiah-dips-to-four-year-low-on-bond-outflows-dollar-strength</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于美元全面反弹和债券大量外流，卢比跌至四年低点，印尼央行对货币市场进行了干预，以稳定卢比汇率。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-02/rupiah-dips-to-four-year-low-on-bond-outflows-dollar-strength</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 02 Apr 2024 02:11:46 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
