      <title>策略师称日本干预将瞄准5日元反弹</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-01/japan-intervention-would-target-five-yen-rally-strategists-say</link>
      <description><![CDATA[日本一些最大经纪公司的策略师表示，如果日本当局决定干预外汇市场，他们的目标可能是日元兑美元上涨 5 倍。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-01/japan-intervention-would-target-five-yen-rally-strategists-say</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Apr 2024 23:31:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
